1
00:00:00,330 --> 00:00:01,330
What were you thinking?!

2
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:15,080
I'm sorry.

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:16,330
It's all my fault.

4
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:16,880
You idiot!

5
00:00:17,250 --> 00:00:19,170
Why didn't you
just run?

6
00:00:19,420 --> 00:00:21,580
I saw everything!
You could have escaped!

7
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:22,830
When he pulled out that box cutter,

8
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:25,790
you should've run
the moment you turned him down!

9
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:27,880
It was obvious
that guy was dangerous.

10
00:00:28,330 --> 00:00:29,330
I'm sorry.

11
00:00:30,630 --> 00:00:32,630
You could have
been killed!

12
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:36,960
I was frozen.

13
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:41,040
I'm sorry.

14
00:00:45,750 --> 00:00:47,330
I'm so glad you're okay.

15
00:00:52,130 --> 00:00:53,330
This girl...

16
00:00:53,330 --> 00:00:54,920
She's just a regular girl after all.
